Whenever I ask you writing a new file, make sure to
- use markdown as the file format

Whenever I ask you writing a new diagram, make sure to
- use excalidraw json format for diagrams

Whenever I ask you writing a new dialogue, make sure to
- use yarn format
- use pascal case for title
- use snake case for variables
- not describe doings, only spoken content or thoughts of characters

Whenever I ask you writing a new script, make sure to
- use GDScript format for the Godot Engine
- use camelCase for function names and variables
- use common patterns for game development